  27,47,"WÕªkaa sŒµ: ‚ÄúWo ne wÕªn a wÕªka wo ho no yŒµ mmusuo ma yŒµn‚Äú. Soalhu kaa sŒµ: ‚ÄùMo mmusuo no fri NyankopÕªn hÕª; daabi, moyŒµ nnipa a mowÕª nsÕªhwŒµ mu ‚Äú."
  27,48,"Na mmarima nkron bi wÕª kuro no mu a wÕªdi nsŒµmmÕªne wÕª asaase no so a wÕªnyŒµ ntotoeŒµ pa."
